01:24:08.220 --> 01:24:09.460
Queen shit, honestly.

01:24:09.460 --> 01:24:12.940
The English suffragette Mary Lee threw a fucking hatchet

01:24:12.940 --> 01:24:14.620
at the Prime Minister's head.

01:24:14.620 --> 01:24:16.860
And my point is not to advocate terrorism

01:24:17.540 --> 01:24:19.540
or to excuse the terrorism of past movements.

01:24:19.540 --> 01:24:21.180
I think these kinds of tactics have tended

01:24:21.180 --> 01:24:23.020
to turn people against the movement.

01:24:23.020 --> 01:24:24.460
I don't think it's effective.

01:24:24.460 --> 01:24:26.660
But let's not pretend that past movements

01:24:26.660 --> 01:24:29.560
have never made demands before everyone was ready.

01:24:29.560 --> 01:24:31.060
Because there never has been,

01:24:31.060 --> 01:24:34.000
