01:24:34.000 --> 01:24:36.220
I mean, Mary Wollstonecraft published

01:24:36.220 --> 01:24:39.540
the Vindication of the Rights of Women in 1792,

01:24:39.540 --> 01:24:43.560
and misogyny, in case you hadn't noticed, remains rampant.

01:24:43.560 --> 01:24:46.420
So there never has been a consensus about women's rights,

01:24:46.460 --> 01:24:48.220
and there probably never will be.

01:24:48.220 --> 01:24:51.620
In fact, marginalized groups wouldn't need rights

01:24:51.620 --> 01:24:54.380
