01:25:03.580 --> 01:25:06.220
but the reality is, that's not how this works,

01:25:06.220 --> 01:25:07.380
and it never has been.

01:25:07.380 --> 01:25:09.580
Like, how do these debate me centrists

01:25:09.580 --> 01:25:12.300
