01:30:55.640 --> 01:30:57.040
if you don't know where this is going,

01:30:57.040 --> 01:30:59.720
strap in from the Bookstart Bear

01:30:59.720 --> 01:31:04.720
to a bright, vibrant, gender-neutral creature called Tala.

01:31:06.200 --> 01:31:08.280
