01:31:14.480 --> 01:31:17.160
who referred to Talia, wait, wasn't it Tala?

01:31:17.160 --> 01:31:21.840
Referring to Talia as a trans bear with they-them pronouns.

01:31:21.840 --> 01:31:24.880
Describing the mascot as ideological,

01:31:24.920 --> 01:31:27.160
creepy, and gaslighting.

01:31:27.160 --> 01:31:30.920
