01:31:41.200 --> 01:31:44.800
Did it hatch from an egg or was it born from a mama?

01:31:44.800 --> 01:31:46.840
Some people tried to reason with Maya.

01:31:46.840 --> 01:31:48.520
There's an advantage in having a character

01:31:48.520 --> 01:31:50.720
that isn't identifiably male or female,

01:31:50.720 --> 01:31:53.000
as it can be equally relatable to either sex

01:31:53.000 --> 01:31:55.200
and avoid promoting gender stereotypes.

01:31:55.200 --> 01:31:57.480
But Maya was not convinced.

01:31:57.480 --> 01:31:59.960
