01:32:03.520 --> 01:32:05.480
is not sexually reproducing.

01:32:05.480 --> 01:32:08.000
It's a relatable anthropomorphic character,

01:32:08.000 --> 01:32:10.400
not a slime mold.

01:32:10.400 --> 01:32:15.280
I need to know how the alien fucks right now.

01:32:15.280 --> 01:32:20.200
I said I need to know how the alien fucks

01:32:20.200 --> 01:32:23.640
before I can show it to my child.

01:32:23.640 --> 01:32:28.640
When Twitter, understandably, laughed it up

01:32:29.080 --> 01:32:32.480
at Maya's expense, she just kept posting.

01:32:32.480 --> 01:32:33.600
And she posted hard.

01:32:33.600 --> 01:32:35.320
Honestly, I don't know if I've ever seen

01:32:35.320 --> 01:32:36.640
anyone post so hard.

01:32:36.640 --> 01:32:38.880
In a lengthy diatribe, Maya wrote about

01:32:38.880 --> 01:32:40.880
