01:32:49.640 --> 01:32:52.200
right and wrong, and you've become invisible.

01:32:52.200 --> 01:32:53.640
You had politics.

01:32:53.640 --> 01:32:54.960
You had a career.

01:32:54.960 --> 01:32:56.520
You had interests.

01:32:56.520 --> 01:32:57.960
You had a sex life.

01:32:57.960 --> 01:32:59.520
Now, you have the daily needs

01:32:59.520 --> 01:33:01.360
of a completely dependent person,

01:33:01.360 --> 01:33:03.000
and your world has shrunk.

01:33:03.000 --> 01:33:05.800
The fact that these men and the young women

01:33:05.800 --> 01:33:08.760
that cheer them on think this is so laughable

01:33:08.760 --> 01:33:11.440
reflects society's disdain for mothers.

01:33:11.440 --> 01:33:12.880
This is what it means to say

01:33:12.880 --> 01:33:15.240
a woman is not a feeling or a costume.

01:33:15.240 --> 01:33:19.120
This is why the hub of the resistance is on Mumsnet.

01:33:19.120 --> 01:33:22.280
So, I am fascinated by this thread.

01:33:22.280 --> 01:33:24.480
I think it's one of the most revealing texts

01:33:24.480 --> 01:33:26.000
in gender-critical history.

01:33:26.000 --> 01:33:27.400
Because you know what?

01:33:27.400 --> 01:33:31.920
